///// sql
{
    - no standart driver, only interface == database/sql:
    _ "github.../mysql" == init registers handlers of interface
    - setMaxOpenConnections == sync protocol, quantity of connections
    - sql.Open() => initialize
    - sql.Ping() => connect to DB
    - always close connections
    - query() => get
    - insert() => post
    - use placeholders
}

